    {
      "id": "optimistic_5_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "optimistic_5",
      "description": "Roll up your sleeves for this incredible opportunity! This vehicle is definitely a diamond in the rough, showing significant wear and needing some mechanical and cosmetic TLC, but it's the perfect project for a budget-conscious DIYer. If you're looking for a solid base to restore or a very affordable way to get on the road with some work, this is the one for you!",
