    {
      "id": "detailed_2_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_2",
      "description": "This vehicle is being sold in poor condition and will require significant work to become roadworthy again. The engine has a noticeable knock and the transmission struggles to engage properly, making it undrivable in its current state. The body shows heavy wear, including several large dents, significant paint peeling, and some rust spots on the undercarriage. This would be an ideal candidate for a dedicated mechanic looking for a project or for someone in need of specific parts.",
