    },
    {
      "id": "detailed_3_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_3",
      "description": "This vehicle is in good condition and has been consistently maintained, making it a reliable choice for any driver. The engine starts up without hesitation and the transmission shifts smoothly through all gears. Inside, the cabin is clean and well-preserved, though you might find some very minor cosmetic wear consistent with careful use. Overall, it offers a comfortable and dependable driving experience with no immediate mechanical concerns.",
